    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Driver Side Storm Window Assembly (Optional)</title>
        <para>When specified, the optional driver side sliding storm window assembly is available. This sliding window
            assembly utilizes a thicker thermal type glass mounted in an aluminum extrusion. The window is mounted in
            the window frame area but has an offset extruded framework to compensate for the glass thickness.
        </para>
    </svcsubproc>
